{"type": "article", "id": 19795, "title": "水泥文具系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-28T07:40:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125720TgnHN80ymiYhwU4I.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t用水泥做的家具或文具小件是近期产品设计的新热点，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/14849.html\" target=\"_blank\">我们曾经报道过本土创造的水泥产品</a>，改变了人们对水泥的冰冷印象，呈现出原始而温柔的特征。这套水泥文具系列来自台湾设计师 Yen-Wen Tseng，有灰色和蓝色两套，包括笔筒、透明胶底座、名片夹。每一件都可以解构出几何原型，或者是在长方体的水泥块中做一个半圆的缺口，或者将圆柱体、正方体等不同的几何体组合在一起，在保留原始感之余有现代设计的特征。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150202ImJqYdENpiDKRLeX.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150202MRtAmVq6lnNL8oEh.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150203VOjwdtqDrCcUzm98.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150204nUCQc2WO3L5lJerw.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}